* # Iron, strong site: Appelo, Van der Weiden, Tournassat & Charlet, subm.
*          Hfo_sOH + Fe+2 = Hfo_sOFe+ + H+
*          log_k   -0.95
* # Iron, weak site: Liger et al., GCA 63, 2939, re-optimized for D&M
